# Implementation

Single-page JavaScript application rendered entirely with HTML5 Canvas 2D context. No external game frameworks or UI libraries. All game logic in vanilla ES modules.

## Technology Stack

- **Language:** Vanilla JavaScript (ES2022, ES modules)
- **Rendering:** HTML5 Canvas 2D context, single `<canvas>` element
- **Bundling:** Vite 5.x for dev server and production build
- **Testing:** Vitest 1.x for unit tests
- **Package manager:** npm
- **No runtime dependencies** apart from dev tooling

